"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-showbiz-tv-radio-1931930-olympics-fans-fed-up-bbc-coverage\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  ManyBBCviewers have been left infuriated by the scaled-down coverage of theParis Olympics 2024which has meant many events have not been shown and a lot of the action has been missed.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For London 2012, the Beeb could show as much action as they wanted through online and red button feeds.\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 190, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999663123168, \"rank\": 3.3687508818028685e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the broadcaster lost control of the rights to the Games in 2015 and is now restricted to showing limited coverage.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The change has sparked a huge backlash from sports fans, which appears to have reached a fever pitch on social media.\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One frustrated viewer tweeted on Sunday: \\\"So fed up with @BBCOlympic coverage - constant switches of channel, focus only on GB competitors, too many pundits and unable to find specific sports/events anywhere!\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9718868633602027, \"rank\": 0.01055870604886669, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is not there an index on iPlayer so you can watch gymnastics/athletics/archery/hockey etc.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"#BBCOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another raged: \\\"Put the Golf on like you promised FFS.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Forces_Front\", \"score\": 0.9998066757624344, \"rank\": 0.0001933616189209515, \"text\": \"FFS\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Forces_Front\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Forces_Front\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your coverage is all over the place!\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#BBCOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:BBC cause fury after turning off Djokovic vs Alcaraz Olympics final during match    A third wrote: \\\"Coverage of the games has been insufferable today.\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 972, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8631900720792148, \"rank\": 0.15849338014427822, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.583803112691224e-17, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just show the god damn sports that are on LIVE!!!\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not want all this recap BS!!\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#BBCOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fourth lamented: \\\"I miss London, Rio etc and having multiple feeds!\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999964556991, \"rank\": 2.945899182872216e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This feels claustrophobic and the BBC controlling what we can watch.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8631900720792148, \"rank\": 0.15849338014427822, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deal is perfect for them!\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Too much chat and not enough (limited) action.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am barely bothered with this compared to before.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#BBCOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While another questioned: \\\"Anyone else annoyed at the BBC coverage of the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8631900720792148, \"rank\": 0.15849338014427822, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They spend most of it talking and switching channels, show you athletics events after they have already happened, and now the golf has just been cut off for cycling and the news\\u2026 can not even get it on iPlayer?\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"#BBCOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And a sixth said: \\\"#bbcolympics you have limited coverage rights so I beg you stop having people talk in a studio giving a nonsense analysis while we have live athletics literally happening in the background.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please show the actual sport @BBCSport.\\\"\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC had to change the way it covers the Olympics after Warner Bros Discovery (WBD) bought the European TV rights in 2015.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8631900720792148, \"rank\": 0.15849338014427822, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2128, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"score\": 0.751507950975948, \"rank\": 0.3306453460271953, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\"}, {\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999581632, \"rank\